&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Maze Therapeutics has&amp;nbsp;an exciting pipeline&amp;nbsp;spanning both rare and common&amp;nbsp;renal, cardiac, and metabolic diseases.&amp;nbsp;In short,&amp;nbsp;you&#39;ll&amp;nbsp;play a fundamental part in advancing&amp;nbsp;medical breakthroughs that have the&amp;nbsp;potential to transform many lives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
